Sophomore Tiffany Gay thought she was being led outside for a routine fire drill but instead she found Luis Velasquez holding a bouquet of flowers . 
 Gay's classmates cheered as she held back tears of joy and some of them held signs that read, 'Will you go to prom with me?'Gay is a special needs student who struggles with a genetic disorder called Prader-Willi Syndrome (PWS)PWS causes insatiable appetite along with other physical abnormalities . 
 Video of the cute promposal has over three million views since being posted to Facebook on Tuesday . 
 